thread.title: Seton Hall 7th in Big East preseason coaches' poll, 2 players preseason All-Big East picks
thread.title_full: Seton Hall 7th in Big East preseason coaches' poll, 2 players preseason All-Big East picks | NJ.com

author: Jeremy Schneider | NJ Advance Media For NJ.com
title: Seton Hall 7th in Big East preseason coaches' poll, 2 players preseason All-Big East picks
text:
NEW YORK — Seton Hall was picked seventh in the Big East preseason coaches' poll, which was released on Wednesday at the league's media day held at Madison Square Garden.
The Pirates, who finished 16-15 last season, also had two players named Preseason All-Big East Second Team selections — forward Angel Delgado, who was the Big East Rookie of the Year last season , and highly touted point guard Isaiah Whitehead.
RELATED: More Seton Hall coverage
Villanova was the unanimous pick to win the Big East for the second straight season after going 33-3 last year, including a 16-2 in-conference mark — w ith one of those losses coming against Seton Hall .
Providence guard Kris Dunn was named the Big East Preseason Player of the Year, while Villanova guard Jalen Brunson was selected the Big East Preseason Freshman of the Year.
